results.name: First occurrence of exactly n 1's in the binary expansion of sqrt(2).
example: The binary expansion of sqrt(2) is 1.0110101000001..(A004539) and at position 17, there are four 1's, framed by 0's, so a(4)=17.
results.author: _Ralf Stephan_, May 18 2003
